<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Giving Tree</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../styles/normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../styles/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Dancing Script">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inter">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Literata">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>
            <div class="cursive">Donate</div>
            <div class="capital-font"> TO THE </div>
            <div class="type-font">GIVING TREE</div>
        </h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="card">
            <h2>You Can Make a difference!</h2>
            <p>As a community you and I will be caring for Kids at Christmastime! I have seen and believe in the power
                of community care and
                compassion. One of the best ways to help is by supporting children during this holiday season, so they
                may experience the warmth of
                Christmas, just like every child should.
            </p>
            <div class="donate-btns">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#donateInstructions" class="button ">Donate Instructions</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="card">
            <h2>How Do I Donate Without the Headache?</h2>
            <h3>Donate Money Directly</h3>
            <p>As a community you and I will be caring for Kids at Christmastime! I have seen and believe in the power
                of community care and
                compassion. One of the best ways to help is by supporting children during this holiday season, so they
                may experience the warmth of
                Christmas, just like every child should.
            </p>
            <div class="donate-btns">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#donateInstructions" class="button ">Donate Instructions</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="card" id="donateInstructions">
            <h2>Donation Instructions</h2>
            <h3>Venmo Instructions</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Set Up Your Own Venmo Account:</strong> If you don't already have a Venmo account, download
                    the Venmo app from
                    your mobile app store or visit the Venmo website. Sign up for an account and link it to your bank
                    account or credit/debit card.</li>
                <li><strong>Find the Recipient's Venmo Username:</strong> You'll need to know the Venmo username or
                    email address of the person or organization you want to donate to. They must also have a Venmo
                    account.</li>
                <li><strong>Open the Venmo App:</strong> Launch the Venmo app on your mobile device or visit the Venmo
                    website in your web browser.</li>
                <li><strong>Initiate a Payment:</strong> In the Venmo app, tap on the "Pay or Request" button, or on the
                    website, click on "Pay or Request" from the main menu.</li>
                <li><strong>Enter the Recipient's Username or Email:</strong> In the "To" field, type in the Venmo
                    username or email address of the recipient to whom you want to donate.</li>
                <li><strong>Enter the Donation Amount:</strong> In the "Amount" field, enter the amount you wish to
                    donate.</li>
                <li><strong>Add a Note (Optional):</strong> You can include a note or a message to specify the purpose
                    of your donation. For example, you can mention it's for a charity, fundraiser, or any other specific
                    cause.</li>
                <li><strong>Choose Your Payment Method:</strong> Select your preferred payment method, either your
                    linked bank account or credit/debit card.</li>
                <li><strong>Review and Confirm:</strong> Double-check the details to ensure they are correct. Then, tap
                    the "Pay" button to confirm the donation.</li>
                <li><strong>Review Transaction:</strong> After confirming, you will see a summary of the transaction.
                    Verify the details one last time, and if everything looks correct, you can proceed to complete the
                    transaction.</li>
                <li><strong>Transaction Confirmation:</strong> Once the transaction is complete, you and the recipient
                    will receive a notification confirming the donation.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <div class="donate-btns">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="/" class="button">Return Home</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/contribute/" class="button">Sponsor Kid</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
<footer>
</footer>

</html>


doctype html
html
  head
    title Gift #{id}
  body
    h1 Gift #{id}
    if img
      img(src=`/images/${img}`, alt=`Gift ${id}`, width="100px")
    if desc
      p Description: #{desc}
    if suggest_price
      p Suggested Price: #{suggest_price}
    if url
      p URL: #{url}

    hr

    form(method="post")
      fieldset 
        legend Claim this Gift
        label(for="commit_price") Price:
        input(type="number", name="commit_price", min=0, step="any")
        if !url
          label(for="url") URL:
          input(type="url", name="url")
        label(for="delivery_msg") Delivery Msg:
        textarea(name="delivery_msg", cols="30", rows="1") 
        label(for="venmo") Venmo:
        input(type="text", name="venmo", required)
        
        input(type="submit", value="Claim")

    hr

    a(href = `${nextUrl}`)
      button Pick a Gift!
    a(href='/contribute/')
      button Contribute Directly